    <item>
      <title>Introduction</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/introduction/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/introduction/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-policy-operator&#34;&gt;What is Policy Operator?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Policy Operator is a Kubernetes-native controller that brings Azure Policy management into the GitOps world. It extends the Kubernetes API with custom resources — giving platform and security teams a declarative, version-controlled way to define, assign, and exempt Azure governance policies without ever leaving the tools they already know.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Instead of clicking through the Azure Portal or running imperative scripts, you write a YAML manifest, open a pull request, and let the operator reconcile the desired state against Azure&amp;rsquo;s Policy API.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Getting Started</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/getting-started/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/getting-started/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;prerequisites&#34;&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Before installing the Policy Operator, ensure you have:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A Kubernetes cluster (v1.24+)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;kubectl&lt;/code&gt; configured against your cluster&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;An Azure subscription with permissions to create and assign policies&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A Service Principal or Managed Identity with the &lt;strong&gt;Resource Policy Contributor&lt;/strong&gt; role&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;installation&#34;&gt;Installation&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-install-with-helm&#34;&gt;1. Install with Helm&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;helm repo add policy-operator https://charts.example.com/policy-operator&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;helm repo update&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;helm install policy-operator policy-operator/policy-operator &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  --namespace policy-system &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  --create-namespace &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  --set azure.tenantId&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;TENANT_ID&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  --set azure.subscriptionId&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;SUBSCRIPTION_ID&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  --set azure.clientId&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;CLIENT_ID&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  --set azure.clientSecret&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;CLIENT_SECRET&amp;gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-verify-installation&#34;&gt;2. Verify installation&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;kubectl get pods -n policy-system&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# NAME                               READY   STATUS    RESTARTS   AGE&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# policy-operator-6d9b4c8f7-xk2lp   1/1     Running   0          30s&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;your-first-policy-definition&#34;&gt;Your first policy definition&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Create a file &lt;code&gt;deny-public-ip.yaml&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>API Reference</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/api-reference/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/api-reference/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;supported-kinds&#34;&gt;Supported Kinds&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The operator manages the following custom resources:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Kind&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;API Version&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyDefinition&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Azure Policy definition&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyInitiative&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Policy set definition&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyAssignment&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Policy / initiative assignment&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyExemption&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Policy exemption&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyRemediation&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Remediation task&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;azurepolicydefinition&#34;&gt;AzurePolicyDefinition&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;: policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;: AzurePolicyDefinition&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: my-policy&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;spec&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;displayName&lt;/span&gt;: string          &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Human-readable name&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt;: string          &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Optional description&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyType: Custom | BuiltIn # Default&lt;/span&gt;: Custom&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;mode: All | Indexed          # Default&lt;/span&gt;: All&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;: {}                 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Arbitrary metadata map&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;parameters&lt;/span&gt;: {}               &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Parameter definitions&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyRule&lt;/span&gt;:                  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Required — the policy rule object&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;: {}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;: {}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;azurepolicyinitiative&#34;&gt;AzurePolicyInitiative&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;: policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;: AzurePolicyInitiative&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: my-initiative&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;spec&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;displayName&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;: {}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;parameters&lt;/span&gt;: {}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyDefinitions&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    - &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyDefinitionId&lt;/span&gt;: string    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# ARM resource ID or CRD name ref&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;      &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;parameters&lt;/span&gt;: {}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;azurepolicyassignment&#34;&gt;AzurePolicyAssignment&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;: policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;: AzurePolicyAssignment&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: my-assignment&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;spec&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;displayName&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;scope&lt;/span&gt;: string               &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# Management group / subscription / resource group ID&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyDefinitionId&lt;/span&gt;: string  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# ARM ID of the definition or initiative&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;parameters&lt;/span&gt;: {}&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;enforcementMode&lt;/span&gt;: Default | DoNotEnforce&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;notScopes&lt;/span&gt;: []               &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# List of resource IDs to exclude&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;azurepolicyexemption&#34;&gt;AzurePolicyExemption&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;: policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;: AzurePolicyExemption&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: my-exemption&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;spec&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;scope&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyAssignmentId&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;exemptionCategory&lt;/span&gt;: Waiver | Mitigated&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;expiresOn&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f1fa8c&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;2026-12-31T00:00:00Z&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# RFC 3339, optional&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;description&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;azurepolicyremediation&#34;&gt;AzurePolicyRemediation&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-yaml&#34; data-lang=&#34;yaml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;: policy.azure.com/v1alpha1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;: AzurePolicyRemediation&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;metadata&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;: my-remediation&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;spec&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;scope&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyAssignmentId&lt;/span&gt;: string&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;policyDefinitionReferenceId&lt;/span&gt;: string  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#6272a4&#34;&gt;# For initiative assignments&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;resourceDiscoveryMode&lt;/span&gt;: ExistingNonCompliant | ReEvaluateCompliance&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;parallelDeployments&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#bd93f9&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;failureThreshold&lt;/span&gt;:&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;percentage&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#bd93f9&#34;&gt;0.1&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Policy Definitions</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-definitions/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-definitions/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyDefinition&lt;/code&gt; custom resource maps directly to an &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/governance/policy/overview&#34;&gt;Azure Policy Definition&lt;/a&gt;. The operator reconciles each resource by creating or updating the corresponding definition in Azure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-schema&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__tabbar&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34; aria-label=&#34;Documentation tabs&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab api-schema__tab--active&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;docs&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;API Documentation&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;examples&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Examples (4)&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__panel&#34; data-schema-panel=&#34;docs&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;api-field-tree&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-field&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button&#xA;    class=&#34;api-field__header&#34;&#xA;    aria-expanded=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;    aria-controls=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396352000&#34;&#xA;    data-api-toggle&#xA;    type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__toggle&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-plus&#34;  width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;5&#34; y1=&#34;1&#34; x2=&#34;5&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-minus&#34; width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__name&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__spacer&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__right&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__type&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__body&#34; id=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396352000&#34; hidden&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__content&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;api-field__desc&#34;&gt;API version for this resource. Must be policy.azure.com/v1alpha1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Policy Initiatives</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-initiatives/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-initiatives/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyInitiative&lt;/code&gt; custom resource maps to an &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/governance/policy/concepts/initiative-definition-structure&#34;&gt;Azure Policy Set Definition&lt;/a&gt;. An initiative groups one or more policy definitions so they can be assigned and tracked together. The operator reconciles each resource by creating or updating the corresponding policy set definition in Azure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-schema&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__tabbar&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34; aria-label=&#34;Documentation tabs&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab api-schema__tab--active&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;docs&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;API Documentation&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;examples&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Examples (4)&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__panel&#34; data-schema-panel=&#34;docs&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;api-field-tree&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-field&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button&#xA;    class=&#34;api-field__header&#34;&#xA;    aria-expanded=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;    aria-controls=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396383000&#34;&#xA;    data-api-toggle&#xA;    type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__toggle&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-plus&#34;  width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;5&#34; y1=&#34;1&#34; x2=&#34;5&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-minus&#34; width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__name&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__spacer&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__right&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__type&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__body&#34; id=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396383000&#34; hidden&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__content&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;api-field__desc&#34;&gt;API version for this resource. Must be policy.azure.com/v1alpha1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Policy Assignments</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-assignments/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-assignments/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyAssignment&lt;/code&gt; custom resource maps to an &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/governance/policy/concepts/assignment-structure&#34;&gt;Azure Policy Assignment&lt;/a&gt;. An assignment binds a policy definition or initiative to a scope (subscription, resource group, or management group) and optionally configures parameters, managed identity, resource selectors, and inline exemptions. The operator reconciles each resource by creating or updating the corresponding assignment in Azure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-schema&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__tabbar&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34; aria-label=&#34;Documentation tabs&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab api-schema__tab--active&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;docs&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;API Documentation&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;examples&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Examples (4)&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__panel&#34; data-schema-panel=&#34;docs&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;api-field-tree&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-field&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button&#xA;    class=&#34;api-field__header&#34;&#xA;    aria-expanded=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;    aria-controls=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396130000&#34;&#xA;    data-api-toggle&#xA;    type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__toggle&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-plus&#34;  width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;5&#34; y1=&#34;1&#34; x2=&#34;5&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-minus&#34; width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__name&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__spacer&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__right&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__type&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__body&#34; id=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396130000&#34; hidden&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__content&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;api-field__desc&#34;&gt;API version for this resource. Must be policy.azure.com/v1alpha1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Policy Exemptions</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-exemptions/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/policy-exemptions/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;AzurePolicyExemption&lt;/code&gt; custom resource maps to an &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/governance/policy/concepts/exemption-structure&#34;&gt;Azure Policy Exemption&lt;/a&gt;. An exemption excludes a resource scope from evaluation under a specific policy assignment — without removing the assignment itself. Common uses include temporary waivers for legacy resources and mitigated exceptions where an alternative control satisfies the policy intent. The operator reconciles each resource by creating or updating the corresponding exemption in Azure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-schema&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__tabbar&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34; aria-label=&#34;Documentation tabs&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab api-schema__tab--active&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;docs&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;API Documentation&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;api-schema__tab&#34;&#xA;      role=&#34;tab&#34;&#xA;      aria-selected=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;      data-schema-tab=&#34;examples&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Examples (4)&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-schema__panel&#34; data-schema-panel=&#34;docs&#34; role=&#34;tabpanel&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;api-field-tree&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;api-field&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;button&#xA;    class=&#34;api-field__header&#34;&#xA;    aria-expanded=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;    aria-controls=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396273000&#34;&#xA;    data-api-toggle&#xA;    type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__toggle&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-plus&#34;  width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;5&#34; y1=&#34;1&#34; x2=&#34;5&#34; y2=&#34;9&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg class=&#34;apf-minus&#34; width=&#34;10&#34; height=&#34;10&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 10 10&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&lt;line x1=&#34;1&#34; y1=&#34;5&#34; x2=&#34;9&#34; y2=&#34;5&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;/&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__name&#34;&gt;apiVersion&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__spacer&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__right&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;api-field__type&#34;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__body&#34; id=&#34;apif-apiversion-1774730698396273000&#34; hidden&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;api-field__content&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;api-field__desc&#34;&gt;API version for this resource. Must be policy.azure.com/v1alpha1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GitOps with Argo CD</title>
      <link>https://policy-operator.io/docs/gitops-argocd/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://policy-operator.io/docs/gitops-argocd/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; The architecture and Argo CD deployment model described on this page is a reference design. Actual implementation will vary based on your organisation&amp;rsquo;s specific requirements, tooling, and platform constraints. Treat this as a starting point, not a prescriptive standard.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;GitOps treats your Git repository as the single source of truth for cluster state. When combined with the Policy Operator, every Azure Policy definition, assignment, exemption, and remediation becomes a versioned, reviewable, auditable Kubernetes manifest — and Argo CD keeps Azure in sync automatically.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
  </channel>
</rss>
